HICKS v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [P. C. No. 18,

September Term, 1959.]

Decided October 20, 1959.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

Per Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal is denied for the reasons set forth in Judge Evans’ opinion below.

Application denied.
